zzapper <david@tvis.co.uk>:
> print ${somevar//[^[:alnum:]]/_}   # replace all non-alphanumerics with _
> 
> But how to delete just a trailing or not carriage return?

cr=$'\r'
print ${foo//${cr}/_}

